299
0:12:23.26,000 --> 0:12:26,000
to places that their genes adapt them to,

300
0:12:26.26,000 --> 0:12:28,000
with social learning and language,

301
0:12:28.26,000 --> 0:12:3,000
we could transform the environment

302
0:12:30.26,000 --> 0:12:32,000
