308
0:12:45.26,000 --> 0:12:48,000
for converting new lands and resources

309
0:12:48.26,000 --> 0:12:51,000
into more people and their genes

310
0:12:51.26,000 --> 0:12:53,000
that natural selection has ever devised.

311
0:12:53.26,000 --> 0:12:55,000
Language really is

312
0:12:55.26,000 --> 0:12:57,000
the voice of our genes.

313
0:12:57.26,000 --> 0:12:59,000
Now having evolved language, though,

314
0:12:59.26,000 --> 0:13:01,000
