327
0:13:32.26,000 --> 0:13:34,000
distinct human languages,

328
0:13:34.26,000 --> 0:13:36,000
different human languages,

329
0:13:36.26,000 --> 0:13:38,000
spoken on that island alone.

330
0:13:38.26,000 --> 0:13:4,000
