339
0:13:59.26,000 --> 0:14:02,000
And this is also true of some remote oceanic islands.

340
0:14:03.26,000 --> 0:14:05,000
And so it seems that we use our language,

341
0:14:05.26,000 --> 0:14:07,000
not just to cooperate,

342
0:14:07.26,000 --> 0:14:1,000
but to draw rings around our cooperative groups

343
0:14:10.26,000 --> 0:14:12,000
and to establish identities,

344
0:14:12.26,000 --> 0:14:15,000
