345
0:14:15.26,000 --> 0:14:18,000
from eavesdropping from outside.

346
0:14:18.26,000 --> 0:14:2,000
And we know this

347
0:14:20.26,000 --> 0:14:22,000
because when we study different language groups

348
0:14:22.26,000 --> 0:14:24,000
and associate them with their cultures,

349
0:14:24.26,000 --> 0:14:26,000
we see that different languages

350
0:14:26.26,000 --> 0:14:29,000
slow the flow of ideas between groups.

351
0:14:29.26,000 --> 0:14:32,000
They slow the flow of technologies.

352
0:14:32.26,000 --> 0:14:35,000
And they even slow the flow of genes.

353
0:14:35.26,000 --> 0:14:37,000
Now I can't speak for you,

354
0:14:37.26,000 --> 0:14:39,000
but it seems to be the case

355
0:14:39.26,000 --> 0:14:42,000
that we don't have sex with people we can't talk to.

