407
0:16:49.26,000 --> 0:16:52,000
And so if language really is

408
0:16:52.26,000 --> 0:16:55,000
the solution to the crisis of visual theft,

409
0:16:55.26,000 --> 0:16:57,000
if language really is

410
0:16:57.26,000 --> 0:16:59,000
the conduit of our cooperation,

411
0:16:59.26,000 --> 0:17:02,000
the technology that our species derived

412
0:17:02.26,000 --> 0:17:06,000
to promote the free flow and exchange of ideas,

413
0:17:06.26,000 --> 0:17:08,000
in our modern world,

